item.title: First Time Street Photography: PhotoWalk in Cebu
item.description: This was a first time experience and somehow it is easier said than done. Getting creative shots on the street is not an easy task. Me and a friend decided to met up in a coffee shop first where they have this unique interior. The meeting place for the Photowalk is at Magellan’s Cross at 11am, it was quite late, so if you’re in the place where it’s hot and humid, pack lightly and use breathable clothes.
